      "name": "Luring Song",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The harpy sings a magical melody, which lasts until the harpy's Concentration ends on it. Teste de Resistência de Sabedoria: CD 11, each Humanoid and Gigante in a 90 m Emanation originating from the harpy when the song starts. O alvo fica com a condição Enfeitiçado until the song ends and repeats the save at the end of each of its turns. While Enfeitiçado, o alvo fica com a condição Incapacitado and ignores the Luring Song of other harpies. If o alvo is more than 1,5 m from the harpy, o alvo moves on its turn toward the harpy by the most direct route, trying to get within 1,5 m of the harpy. It doesn't avoid Opportunity Attacks; however, before moving into damaging terrain (such as lava or a pit) and whenever it takes de dano from a source other than the harpy, o alvo repeats the save. O alvo is immune to this harpy's Luring Song for 24 hours.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
